                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.6363 Standard Oil/428: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Engert</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-01-20T11:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 20, 1940—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>8. The substance of your 11, January 17, 11 a.m., has been transmitted to the
                    Standard Oil Company of New Jersey.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
